Sikhs can't even do the last funeral ritual, i.e. the cremation, in Iran. how are then they envied? such false report is not accepted by genuine Sikhs and Sikh community. Second, I made grammar correction: Gurdwara, not gurdwara. and 2 extra spaces. Third, I put the fact that Sikhism is not recognized in Iran supported by citation.
